						and others.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="hyt-pillar-card">
					<span class="hyt-pillar-number">Pillar 04</span>
					<h3>Faith Integration &amp; TRET</h3>
					<p>
						Trauma Resolution Energy Therapy (TRET) is an excellent technique for addressing
						unconscious trauma that affects your physical health. Barbara does not practice
						medicine; however, when you heal the emotions, your body often follows. Trauma affects
						your emotions and your physical health. Barbara applies a Christ-centered approach when
						using this energy technique, as devout Christians are sometimes concerned about any
						technique that is energy related. Barbara is, as well. Therefore, only those techniques
						that can be supported by Scripture are used. Clients have experienced wonderful
						breakthroughs with this technique, even biblical deliverance. God designed the human
						body to be able to release itself from trauma. Barbara will show you how if you are
						interested in applying this technique (optional).
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="hyt-pillar-card">
					<span class="hyt-pillar-number">Pillar 05</span>
					<h3>Judicial Prayer</h3>
					<p>
